Header: Ja Ela Robbery: suspect arrested in Yatiyantota
Content: A suspect who was involved in robbing salary money of Rs.7.5 million  in Ja Ela a few months ago, has been arrested in the Paraswella area in Yatiyantota on Friday evening. The suspect is a 35 year old  resident of  Thanamalwila. The police has also uncovered a sum of  Rs.85, 000 in the suspects possession.
